Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(0,300)\fs15\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(0,200,\fs50)\move(1032,16,491.2,324.8,25,317)}奥德莉·布德罗
